From 13b48afbddf53cc8eab91196e358b22115732fed Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Sun, 15 Feb 2026 06:21:10 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 09/42] Rename One Profile to Chromium Profile Server
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

A name is just a name, they say,
But "One Profile" has had its day.
Five hundred seventy-seven swaps,
A hundred ten files, no half-stops.
From PoC constraint to proper noun—
Chromium Profile Server wears the crown.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
